flowchart TD
    A[Inicio de operación RAG] --> B[Generar request_id]
    B --> C[Generar correlation_id]
    C --> D[Generar transaction_id]
    D --> E[Registrar contexto de operación]

    E --> F{Tipo de operación}

    F -->|Carga documento| G[action_name: document_upload]
    F -->|Procesamiento| H[action_name: document_processing]
    F -->|Chat IA personal| I[action_name: notebook_question_answering]
    F -->|Chat IA sala| J[action_name: study_room_question_answering]
    F -->|Resumen| K[action_name: summary_generation]
    F -->|Flashcards| L[action_name: flashcards_generation]
    F -->|Mock test| M[action_name: mock_test_generation]

    G --> N[Guardar evento en logs]
    H --> N
    I --> N
    J --> N
    K --> N
    L --> N
    M --> N

    N --> O[Registrar module_name]
    O --> P[Registrar entity_type y entity_id]
    P --> Q[Registrar request_payload]
    Q --> R[Registrar response_payload]
    R --> S{Ocurrió error?}

    S -->|Sí| T[Guardar error_details]
    S -->|No| U[Guardar status_code y latency_ms]

    T --> V[Finalizar trazabilidad]
    U --> V